Open game.html in any browser.
How to play..
1)press start button..your timer starts...total time allowed is 25 sec.
2)after that press play button..enable sound in your device.
3)a word will be pronounced there.
4)once you pause or stop that pronounce part alphabets will start popping up from different sides of the device.
5)you need to select alphabets in the sequence such that when all alphabets selected concatenated in the same 
sequence results same spelling as the pronounced word.
6)If concatenations spells the same as pronounced word then you will be awarded with 1 point, else 0 point.
7)YOUR TASK IS TO COLLECT MAX POINTS IN THE GIVEN TIME.
THERE IS NO WINNING OR LOSING CONDITION,ONLY TOTAL POINTS MATTER.
